The paper deals with image retrieval using deep hashing methods, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed approach involves learning class-wise weights, which is a machine learning task and falls under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves experiments on datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the approach involves fusing semantic probability, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
